Kind: captions
Language: pt-PT

00:00:04.609 --> 00:00:06.578
Der gutherzige schwule Mann Genichi Hatano

00:00:06.644 --> 00:00:08.513
und sein Partner, Saku Sakuta,

00:00:08.580 --> 00:00:10.748
